   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "## Phase 3 — Final Pre-Production Test\n",
    "\n",
    "Applying the trained model to 10 unknown customer records (2 of which are attrited — ~20% ratio). This simulates real-world production scoring for The Great One Bank."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Load 10 unknown Phase 3 records\n",
    "phase3 = pd.read_csv('/content/drive/MyDrive/BankChurner/Phase_3_Records.csv')\n",
    "\n",
    "# Apply same preprocessing as training data\n",
    "phase3 = phase3.drop(columns=['CLIENTNUM'], errors='ignore')\n",
    "phase3_encoded = pd.get_dummies(phase3)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Align columns with training data\n",
    "phase3_encoded = phase3_encoded.reindex(columns=X.columns, fill_value=0)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Predict\n",
    "predictions = best_rf.predict(phase3_encoded)\n",
    "probabilities = best_rf.predict_proba(phase3_encoded)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Display results\n",
    "results = pd.DataFrame({\n",
    "    'Prediction': ['Attrited Customer' if p == 0 else 'Existing Customer' for p in predictions],\n",
    "    'Confidence': [max(prob) for prob in probabilities]\n",
    "})\n",
    "\n",
    "print(results)\n",
    "print(f\"\\nAttrited: {sum(predictions == 0)} / {len(predictions)} ({sum(predictions == 0)/len(predictions)*100:.1f}%)\")\n",
    "print(\"Expected: ~20% attrited (2 out of 10)\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "## Summary of Results\n",
    "\n",
    "| Model | Accuracy | Precision | Recall |\n",
    "|---|---|---|---|\n",
    "| Decision Tree (baseline) | 92.89% | 67.24% | 75.00% |\n",
    "| **Random Forest (recommended)** | **95.33%** | **96.85%** | **97.88%** |\n",
    "| Random Forest (optimized) | **95.33%** | **96.85%** | **97.88%** |\n",
    "\n",
